                    <cell>
                        <line><alert>Scaffolding:</alert> Provide a step-by-step guide for finding reciprocals. Use calculators to verify division. Start with simple whole numbers before moving to decimals and fractions. Work with this group during the anchor task..</line>
                    </cell>
