                        <line><alert>Extension Learning Experience:</alert> A cyclist covers 12 km in 1 hour. A factory machine produces 5/8 of a widget per minute. A typist types 4/7 of a page in 8 minutes. Solve all three word problems and create your own real-world problem involving reciprocals.</line>
                    </cell>
                    <cell></cell>
